CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Diagnosis - Count - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Diagnosis - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[Diagnosis - Count]
	)
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Regular Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='Diagnosis';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Diagnosis - Count - Tied Rank]
as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Diagnosis - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[Diagnosis - Count - Regular Rank], 
        GENERATE(
            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Diagnosis - Count], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,
                    {}
                ),
                ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Diagnosis - Count], BDESC)
            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[Diagnosis - Count]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[Diagnosis - Count]),
                IIF(
                    (PREVATTRIB.ITEM(0), [Measures].[Diagnosis - Count]) = (FIRSTTIE.ITEM(0), [Measures].[Diagnosis - Count])
                    ,{FIRSTTIE}
                    ,{PREVATTRIB AS FIRSTTIE}
                ),
                {CURRATTRIB}
            ),
            ALL
        ).ITEM([Measures].[Diagnosis - Count - Regular Rank]-1)
    )
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Tied Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='Diagnosis';

AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Advance Directive Printed to ED Discharge in Minutes - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER

    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[ED Visit - Advance Directive Printed to ED Discharge in Minutes - Count]

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[ED Visit - Advance Directive Printed to ED Discharge in Minutes - Geometric Average - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Advance Directive Printed to ED Discharge in Minutes - Geometric Average])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[ED Visit - Advance Directive Printed to ED Discharge in Minutes - Geometric Average]
	)
)

as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Advance Directive Printed to ED Discharge in Minutes - Geometric Average])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[ED Visit - Advance Directive Printed to ED Discharge in Minutes - Geometric Average - Regular Rank],

            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[ED Visit - Advance Directive Printed to ED Discharge in Minutes - Geometric Average], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,

            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Advance Directive Printed to ED Discharge in Minutes - Geometric Average]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Advance Directive Printed to ED Discharge in Minutes - Geometric Average]),

                    ,{PREVATTRIB AS FIRSTTIE}

            ALL

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Arithmetic Average - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Arithmetic Average])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Arithmetic Average]
	)
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Regular Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='ED Visit';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Arithmetic Average - Tied Rank]
as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Arithmetic Average])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Arithmetic Average - Regular Rank], 
        GENERATE(
            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Arithmetic Average], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,
                    {}

                ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Arithmetic Average], BDESC)
            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Arithmetic Average]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Arithmetic Average]),
                IIF(

                    ,{FIRSTTIE}
                    ,{PREVATTRIB AS FIRSTTIE}
                ),
                {CURRATTRIB}
            ),
            ALL
        ).ITEM([Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Arithmetic Average - Regular Rank]-1)
    )
)

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Count - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Count]
	)
)

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Count - Tied Rank]
as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Count - Regular Rank], 
        GENERATE(
            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Count], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,
                    {}
                ),
                ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Count], BDESC)
            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Count]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Count]),

                    ,{FIRSTTIE}
                    ,{PREVATTRIB AS FIRSTTIE}
                ),
                {CURRATTRIB}
            ),
            ALL
        ).ITEM([Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Count - Regular Rank]-1)
    )
)

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Geomotric Average - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Geomotric Average])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Geomotric Average]
	)
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Regular Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='ED Visit';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Geomotric Average - Tied Rank]
as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Geomotric Average])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Geomotric Average - Regular Rank], 
        GENERATE(
            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Geomotric Average], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,
                    {}
                ),
                ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Geomotric Average], BDESC)
            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Geomotric Average]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Geomotric Average]),
                IIF(
                    (PREVATTRIB.ITEM(0), [Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Geomotric Average]) = (FIRSTTIE.ITEM(0), [Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Geomotric Average])
                    ,{FIRSTTIE}
                    ,{PREVATTRIB AS FIRSTTIE}
                ),
                {CURRATTRIB}
            ),
            ALL
        ).ITEM([Measures].[ED Visit - Attending Provider Assigned to Disposition in Minutes - Geomotric Average - Regular Rank]-1)
    )
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Tied Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='ED Visit';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[ED Visit - Bed Request to Patient Roomed in Minutes - Count - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Bed Request to Patient Roomed in Minutes - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[ED Visit - Bed Request to Patient Roomed in Minutes - Count]

)

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[ED Visit - Count - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[ED Visit - Count]
	)
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Regular Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='ED Visit';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[ED Visit - Count - Tied Rank]
as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[ED Visit - Count - Regular Rank], 
        GENERATE(
            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[ED Visit - Count], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,
                    {}
                ),
                ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[ED Visit - Count], BDESC)
            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Count]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Count]),
                IIF(
                    (PREVATTRIB.ITEM(0), [Measures].[ED Visit - Count]) = (FIRSTTIE.ITEM(0), [Measures].[ED Visit - Count])
                    ,{FIRSTTIE}
                    ,{PREVATTRIB AS FIRSTTIE}
                ),
                {CURRATTRIB}
            ),
            ALL
        ).ITEM([Measures].[ED Visit - Count - Regular Rank]-1)
    )
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Tied Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='ED Visit';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[ED Visit - Disposition to ED Discharge in Minutes - Count - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Disposition to ED Discharge in Minutes - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[ED Visit - Disposition to ED Discharge in Minutes - Count]
	)
)

        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER

    NULL,
	RANK(

    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Image Completed to Provider Reviewed in Minutes - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER

    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Lab Ordered to Lab Completed in Miinutes - Count])=0

    NULL,
	RANK(

as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Lab Ordered to Lab Completed in Miinutes - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER

            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Lab Ordered to Lab Completed in Miinutes - Count]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Lab Ordered to Lab Completed in Miinutes - Count]),

	RANK(

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Discharge in Minutes - Count - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Discharge in Minutes - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Discharge in Minutes - Count]
	)
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Regular Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='ED Visit';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Discharge in Minutes - Count - Tied Rank]
as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Discharge in Minutes - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Discharge in Minutes - Count - Regular Rank], 
        GENERATE(
            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Discharge in Minutes - Count], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,
                    {}
                ),
                ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Discharge in Minutes - Count], BDESC)
            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Discharge in Minutes - Count]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Discharge in Minutes - Count]),
                IIF(
                    (PREVATTRIB.ITEM(0), [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Discharge in Minutes - Count]) = (FIRSTTIE.ITEM(0), [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Discharge in Minutes - Count])
                    ,{FIRSTTIE}
                    ,{PREVATTRIB AS FIRSTTIE}
                ),
                {CURRATTRIB}
            ),
            ALL
        ).ITEM([Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Discharge in Minutes - Count - Regular Rank]-1)
    )

        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER

		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }),

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Image Ordered in Minutes - Count - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Image Ordered in Minutes - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Image Ordered in Minutes - Count]
	)
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Regular Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='ED Visit';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Image Ordered in Minutes - Count - Tied Rank]
as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Image Ordered in Minutes - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Image Ordered in Minutes - Count - Regular Rank], 
        GENERATE(
            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Image Ordered in Minutes - Count], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,
                    {}
                ),
                ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Image Ordered in Minutes - Count], BDESC)
            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Image Ordered in Minutes - Count]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Image Ordered in Minutes - Count]),
                IIF(
                    (PREVATTRIB.ITEM(0), [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Image Ordered in Minutes - Count]) = (FIRSTTIE.ITEM(0), [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Image Ordered in Minutes - Count])
                    ,{FIRSTTIE}
                    ,{PREVATTRIB AS FIRSTTIE}
                ),
                {CURRATTRIB}
            ),
            ALL
        ).ITEM([Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Image Ordered in Minutes - Count - Regular Rank]-1)
    )
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Tied Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='ED Visit';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Lab Ordered in Minutes - Count - Tied Rank]
as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Lab Ordered in Minutes - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Lab Ordered in Minutes - Count - Regular Rank], 
        GENERATE(
            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Lab Ordered in Minutes - Count], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,
                    {}
                ),
                ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Lab Ordered in Minutes - Count], BDESC)
            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Lab Ordered in Minutes - Count]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Lab Ordered in Minutes - Count]),
                IIF(
                    (PREVATTRIB.ITEM(0), [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Lab Ordered in Minutes - Count]) = (FIRSTTIE.ITEM(0), [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Lab Ordered in Minutes - Count])
                    ,{FIRSTTIE}
                    ,{PREVATTRIB AS FIRSTTIE}
                ),
                {CURRATTRIB}
            ),
            ALL
        ).ITEM([Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Lab Ordered in Minutes - Count - Regular Rank]-1)
    )
)

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Registration Completed in Minutes - Count - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Registration Completed in Minutes - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Registration Completed in Minutes - Count]
	)
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Regular Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='ED Visit';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Registration Completed in Minutes - Count - Tied Rank]
as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Registration Completed in Minutes - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Registration Completed in Minutes - Count - Regular Rank], 
        GENERATE(
            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Registration Completed in Minutes - Count], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,
                    {}
                ),
                ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Registration Completed in Minutes - Count], BDESC)
            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Registration Completed in Minutes - Count]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Registration Completed in Minutes - Count]),

                    ,{PREVATTRIB AS FIRSTTIE}
                ),
                {CURRATTRIB}
            ),
            ALL
        ).ITEM([Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Arrival to Registration Completed in Minutes - Count - Regular Rank]-1)
    )

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Unique Count - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Unique Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Unique Count]
	)
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Regular Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='ED Visit - Patient';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Unique Count - Tied Rank]
as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Unique Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Unique Count - Regular Rank], 
        GENERATE(
            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Unique Count], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,
                    {}
                ),
                ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Unique Count], BDESC)
            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Unique Count]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Unique Count]),
                IIF(
                    (PREVATTRIB.ITEM(0), [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Unique Count]) = (FIRSTTIE.ITEM(0), [Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Unique Count])
                    ,{FIRSTTIE}
                    ,{PREVATTRIB AS FIRSTTIE}
                ),
                {CURRATTRIB}
            ),
            ALL
        ).ITEM([Measures].[ED Visit - Patient Unique Count - Regular Rank]-1)
    )
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Tied Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='ED Visit - Patient';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[ED Visit - Triage Start to Patient Roomed in Minutes - Count - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Triage Start to Patient Roomed in Minutes - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[ED Visit - Triage Start to Patient Roomed in Minutes - Count]
	)
)

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[ED Visit - Triage Start to Patient Roomed in Minutes - Count - Tied Rank]
as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Triage Start to Patient Roomed in Minutes - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,

                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[ED Visit - Triage Start to Patient Roomed in Minutes - Count], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,

            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Triage Start to Patient Roomed in Minutes - Count]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Triage Start to Patient Roomed in Minutes - Count]),

                {CURRATTRIB}
            ),
            ALL
        ).ITEM([Measures].[ED Visit - Triage Start to Patient Roomed in Minutes - Count - Regular Rank]-1)
    )

    ([Measures].[ED Visit - Triage Start to Triage Complete in Minutes - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[ED Visit - Triage Start to Triage Complete in Minutes - Count - Regular Rank], 
        GENERATE(
            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[ED Visit - Triage Start to Triage Complete in Minutes - Count], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,

                ),
                ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[ED Visit - Triage Start to Triage Complete in Minutes - Count], BDESC)
            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Triage Start to Triage Complete in Minutes - Count]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[ED Visit - Triage Start to Triage Complete in Minutes - Count]),

                    ,{FIRSTTIE}
                    ,{PREVATTRIB AS FIRSTTIE}
                ),
                {CURRATTRIB}
            ),
            ALL
        ).ITEM([Measures].[ED Visit - Triage Start to Triage Complete in Minutes - Count - Regular Rank]-1)

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Inpatient - Count - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Inpatient - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[Inpatient - Count]
	)
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Regular Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='Inpatient';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Inpatient - Count - Tied Rank]
as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Inpatient - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[Inpatient - Count - Regular Rank], 
        GENERATE(
            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Inpatient - Count], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,
                    {}
                ),
                ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Inpatient - Count], BDESC)
            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[Inpatient - Count]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[Inpatient - Count]),
                IIF(
                    (PREVATTRIB.ITEM(0), [Measures].[Inpatient - Count]) = (FIRSTTIE.ITEM(0), [Measures].[Inpatient - Count])
                    ,{FIRSTTIE}
                    ,{PREVATTRIB AS FIRSTTIE}
                ),
                {CURRATTRIB}
            ),
            ALL
        ).ITEM([Measures].[Inpatient - Count - Regular Rank]-1)
    )
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Tied Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='Inpatient';

                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Inpatient - Fractional LOS in Hours - Arithmetic Average], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Inpatient - Patient Unique Count - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Inpatient - Patient Unique Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[Inpatient - Patient Unique Count]
	)
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Regular Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='Inpatient - Patient';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Inpatient - Patient Unique Count - Tied Rank]
as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Inpatient - Patient Unique Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[Inpatient - Patient Unique Count - Regular Rank], 
        GENERATE(
            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Inpatient - Patient Unique Count], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,
                    {}
                ),
                ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Inpatient - Patient Unique Count], BDESC)

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Lab Component Result - Patient - Unique Count - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Lab Component Result - Patient - Unique Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[Lab Component Result - Patient - Unique Count]
	)
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Regular Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='Lab Component Result - Patient';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Lab Component Result - Patient - Unique Count - Tied Rank]
as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Lab Component Result - Patient - Unique Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[Lab Component Result - Patient - Unique Count - Regular Rank], 
        GENERATE(
            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Lab Component Result - Patient - Unique Count], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,
                    {}
                ),
                ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Lab Component Result - Patient - Unique Count], BDESC)
            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[Lab Component Result - Patient - Unique Count]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[Lab Component Result - Patient - Unique Count]),
                IIF(
                    (PREVATTRIB.ITEM(0), [Measures].[Lab Component Result - Patient - Unique Count]) = (FIRSTTIE.ITEM(0), [Measures].[Lab Component Result - Patient - Unique Count])
                    ,{FIRSTTIE}
                    ,{PREVATTRIB AS FIRSTTIE}
                ),
                {CURRATTRIB}
            ),
            ALL
        ).ITEM([Measures].[Lab Component Result - Patient - Unique Count - Regular Rank]-1)
    )
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Tied Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='Lab Component Result - Patient';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Lab Order - Count - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Lab Order - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[Lab Order - Count]
	)
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Regular Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='Lab Order';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Lab Order - Count - Tied Rank]
as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Lab Order - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[Lab Order - Count - Regular Rank], 
        GENERATE(
            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Lab Order - Count], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,
                    {}
                ),
                ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Lab Order - Count], BDESC)
            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[Lab Order - Count]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[Lab Order - Count]),
                IIF(
                    (PREVATTRIB.ITEM(0), [Measures].[Lab Order - Count]) = (FIRSTTIE.ITEM(0), [Measures].[Lab Order - Count])
                    ,{FIRSTTIE}
                    ,{PREVATTRIB AS FIRSTTIE}
                ),
                {CURRATTRIB}
            ),
            ALL
        ).ITEM([Measures].[Lab Order - Count - Regular Rank]-1)
    )
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Tied Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='Lab Order';

AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Lab Order - Encounter - Unique Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[Lab Order - Encounter - Unique Count]
	)
)

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Lab Order - Encounter - Unique Count - Tied Rank]
as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Lab Order - Encounter - Unique Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[Lab Order - Encounter - Unique Count - Regular Rank], 
        GENERATE(
            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Lab Order - Encounter - Unique Count], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,
                    {}
                ),
                ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Lab Order - Encounter - Unique Count], BDESC)
            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[Lab Order - Encounter - Unique Count]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[Lab Order - Encounter - Unique Count]),
                IIF(
                    (PREVATTRIB.ITEM(0), [Measures].[Lab Order - Encounter - Unique Count]) = (FIRSTTIE.ITEM(0), [Measures].[Lab Order - Encounter - Unique Count])
                    ,{FIRSTTIE}
                    ,{PREVATTRIB AS FIRSTTIE}
                ),
                {CURRATTRIB}
            ),
            ALL
        ).ITEM([Measures].[Lab Order - Encounter - Unique Count - Regular Rank]-1)
    )
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Tied Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='Lab Order - Encounter';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Medication Administration - Count - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Medication Administration - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[Medication Administration - Count]
	)
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Regular Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='Medication Administration';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Medication Administration - Count - Tied Rank]
as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Medication Administration - Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[Medication Administration - Count - Regular Rank], 
        GENERATE(
            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Medication Administration - Count], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,
                    {}
                ),
                ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Medication Administration - Count], BDESC)
            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[Medication Administration - Count]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[Medication Administration - Count]),
                IIF(
                    (PREVATTRIB.ITEM(0), [Measures].[Medication Administration - Count]) = (FIRSTTIE.ITEM(0), [Measures].[Medication Administration - Count])
                    ,{FIRSTTIE}
                    ,{PREVATTRIB AS FIRSTTIE}
                ),
                {CURRATTRIB}
            ),
            ALL
        ).ITEM([Measures].[Medication Administration - Count - Regular Rank]-1)
    )
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Tied Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='Medication Administration';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Medication Administration - Encounter - Unique Count - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Medication Administration - Encounter - Unique Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[Medication Administration - Encounter - Unique Count]
	)
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Regular Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='Medication Administration - Encounter';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Medication Administration - Encounter - Unique Count - Tied Rank]
as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Medication Administration - Encounter - Unique Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[Medication Administration - Encounter - Unique Count - Regular Rank], 
        GENERATE(
            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Medication Administration - Encounter - Unique Count], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,
                    {}
                ),
                ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Medication Administration - Encounter - Unique Count], BDESC)
            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[Medication Administration - Encounter - Unique Count]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[Medication Administration - Encounter - Unique Count]),
                IIF(
                    (PREVATTRIB.ITEM(0), [Measures].[Medication Administration - Encounter - Unique Count]) = (FIRSTTIE.ITEM(0), [Measures].[Medication Administration - Encounter - Unique Count])
                    ,{FIRSTTIE}
                    ,{PREVATTRIB AS FIRSTTIE}
                ),
                {CURRATTRIB}
            ),
            ALL
        ).ITEM([Measures].[Medication Administration - Encounter - Unique Count - Regular Rank]-1)
    )
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Tied Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='Medication Administration - Encounter';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Medication Order - Encounter - Unique Count - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Medication Order - Encounter - Unique Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[Medication Order - Encounter - Unique Count]
	)
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Regular Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='Medication Order - Encounter';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Medication Order - Encounter - Unique Count - Tied Rank]
as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Medication Order - Encounter - Unique Count])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[Medication Order - Encounter - Unique Count - Regular Rank], 
        GENERATE(
            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Medication Order - Encounter - Unique Count], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,
                    {}
                ),
                ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Medication Order - Encounter - Unique Count], BDESC)
            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[Medication Order - Encounter - Unique Count]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[Medication Order - Encounter - Unique Count]),
                IIF(
                    (PREVATTRIB.ITEM(0), [Measures].[Medication Order - Encounter - Unique Count]) = (FIRSTTIE.ITEM(0), [Measures].[Medication Order - Encounter - Unique Count])
                    ,{FIRSTTIE}
                    ,{PREVATTRIB AS FIRSTTIE}
                ),
                {CURRATTRIB}
            ),
            ALL
        ).ITEM([Measures].[Medication Order - Encounter - Unique Count - Regular Rank]-1)
    )
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Tied Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='Medication Order - Encounter';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Medication Order Quantity - Sum - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Medication Order Quantity - Sum])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[Medication Order Quantity - Sum]
	)
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Regular Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='Medication Order';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Medication Order Quantity - Sum - Tied Rank]
as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Medication Order Quantity - Sum])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[Medication Order Quantity - Sum - Regular Rank], 
        GENERATE(
            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Medication Order Quantity - Sum], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,
                    {}
                ),
                ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Medication Order Quantity - Sum], BDESC)
            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[Medication Order Quantity - Sum]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[Medication Order Quantity - Sum]),
                IIF(
                    (PREVATTRIB.ITEM(0), [Measures].[Medication Order Quantity - Sum]) = (FIRSTTIE.ITEM(0), [Measures].[Medication Order Quantity - Sum])
                    ,{FIRSTTIE}
                    ,{PREVATTRIB AS FIRSTTIE}
                ),
                {CURRATTRIB}
            ),
            ALL
        ).ITEM([Measures].[Medication Order Quantity - Sum - Regular Rank]-1)
    )
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Tied Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='Medication Order';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Ratio Lab Order to Encounter - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Ratio Lab Order to Encounter])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[Ratio Lab Order to Encounter]
	)
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Regular Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='Lab Order';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Ratio Lab Order to Encounter - Tied Rank]
as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Ratio Lab Order to Encounter])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[Ratio Lab Order to Encounter - Regular Rank], 
        GENERATE(
            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Ratio Lab Order to Encounter], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,
                    {}
                ),
                ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Ratio Lab Order to Encounter], BDESC)
            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[Ratio Lab Order to Encounter]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[Ratio Lab Order to Encounter]),
                IIF(
                    (PREVATTRIB.ITEM(0), [Measures].[Ratio Lab Order to Encounter]) = (FIRSTTIE.ITEM(0), [Measures].[Ratio Lab Order to Encounter])
                    ,{FIRSTTIE}
                    ,{PREVATTRIB AS FIRSTTIE}
                ),
                {CURRATTRIB}
            ),
            ALL
        ).ITEM([Measures].[Ratio Lab Order to Encounter - Regular Rank]-1)
    )
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Tied Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='Lab Order';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Ratio Medication to Encounter - Regular Rank]
AS 
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Ratio Medication to Encounter])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
	RANK(
		Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER, 
		except(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.members, { Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER, Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER }), 
		[Measures].[Ratio Medication to Encounter]
	)
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Regular Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='Medication Order';

CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[Measures].[Ratio Medication to Encounter - Tied Rank]
as
IIF(
    ([Measures].[Ratio Medication to Encounter])=0
        or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.DEFAULTMEMBER
	    or Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.CURRENTMEMBER is Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.UNKNOWNMEMBER,
    NULL,
    (
        [Measures].[Ratio Medication to Encounter - Regular Rank], 
        GENERATE(
            {
                INTERSECT(
                    {ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Ratio Medication to Encounter], BDESC).ITEM(0)} AS FIRSTTIE,
                    {}
                ),
                ORDER(Axis(1).Item(0).Item(Axis(1).Item(0).Count - 1).Hierarchy.MEMBERS, [Measures].[Ratio Medication to Encounter], BDESC)
            } AS [OrderedSet2], 
            IIF(
                ({[OrderedSet2].CURRENT AS CURRATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[Ratio Medication to Encounter]) = ({[OrderedSet2].ITEM([OrderedSet2].CURRENTORDINAL-2) AS PREVATTRIB}.ITEM(0),[Measures].[Ratio Medication to Encounter]),
                IIF(
                    (PREVATTRIB.ITEM(0), [Measures].[Ratio Medication to Encounter]) = (FIRSTTIE.ITEM(0), [Measures].[Ratio Medication to Encounter])
                    ,{FIRSTTIE}
                    ,{PREVATTRIB AS FIRSTTIE}
                ),
                {CURRATTRIB}
            ),
            ALL
        ).ITEM([Measures].[Ratio Medication to Encounter - Regular Rank]-1)
    )
)
,VISIBLE=1, DISPLAY_FOLDER='Rank\Tied Rank', FORMAT_STRING='#,##0', ASSOCIATED_MEASURE_GROUP='Medication Order';
